{"article_id":"KzFbYEWbXMijQzUH","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"( CNN ) -","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"Republicans would n't say definitively on Sunday","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"whether presumptive GOP nominee Mitt Romney was facing a problem with voters skeptical about his health care law in Massachusetts ,","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"which bears resemblance to President Barack Obama 's measure .","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"Sen. Mitch McConnell , the top Republican in the U.S. Senate , said simply","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"that Romney would `` have to speak for himself ''","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"when it comes to the Massachusetts law ,","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"which","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"members of Obama 's administration have said","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"was the model for their own legislation .","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"McConnell made a point","depth":12},{"id":11,"text":"of referring to Obama 's penalty for people","depth":13},{"id":12,"text":"who do not obtain health insurance","depth":13},{"id":13,"text":"as a `` tax , '' a term","depth":12},{"id":14,"text":"made possible by the Thursday Supreme Court decision","depth":13},{"id":15,"text":"to uphold the mandate under Congress ' power","depth":14},{"id":16,"text":"to levy taxes .","depth":14},{"id":17,"text":"`` I can tell you","depth":12},{"id":18,"text":"that every single Democratic senator voted for this tax increase , ''","depth":12},{"id":19,"text":"McConnell said on `` Fox News Sunday . ''","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"The tax penalty in the president 's health care law ,","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"which will be administered through the Internal Revenue Service ,","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"is similar to a provision in the reform plan","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"passed in Massachusetts under then-Gov . Mitt Romney .","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"In a 2009 interview with CNN , Romney explained","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"how the Massachusetts health care mandate worked .","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"If a state resident decided to forgo health insurance","depth":15},{"id":27,"text":"when he or she could afford it ,","depth":15},{"id":28,"text":"Romney said ,","depth":14},{"id":29,"text":"that person would face the loss of a tax exemption .","depth":13},{"id":30,"text":"In other words , he or she would be assessed a tax penalty .","depth":12},{"id":31,"text":"`` There are a number of ways","depth":14},{"id":32,"text":"to encourage people to get insurance","depth":14},{"id":33,"text":"and what we did , we said :","depth":14},{"id":34,"text":"'You 're going to lose a tax exemption","depth":15},{"id":35,"text":"if you do n't have insurance , ' ''","depth":15},{"id":36,"text":"Romney told CNN in the interview .","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"The former Massachusetts governor said","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"the mandate was necessary","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"to achieve universal coverage in the state .","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"In order to qualify for the tax exemption ,","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"Romney added ,","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"`` You 've got to have health insurance ,","depth":13},{"id":43,"text":"because we want everybody in the system .","depth":13},{"id":44,"text":"No more free riders . ''","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"During the interview Romney held up his health care law as a model","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"that `` could inform Washington on ways","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"to improve health care for all Americans . ''","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"Since then , Romney has said repeatedly","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"his plan was meant for Massachusetts only .","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"On Sunday , Louisiana Gov . Bobby Jindal backed Romney 's point ,","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"saying","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"the GOP presidential candidate had always been opposed to a national mandate .","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"`` Look , states are different , ''","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"Jindal said .","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"`` The Founding Fathers intended states to be a laboratory of experimentation .","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"I come from one of the most distinct cultural states in the entire country .","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"Mardi Gras is great for Louisiana","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"- may not work as well in Vermont and other states .","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"The idea is ,","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"what works in Massachusetts may not work in another state . ''","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"Republican House Speaker John Boehner made a similar argument ,","depth":6},{"id":62,"text":"saying","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"Romney 's law was `` an issue","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"that was in Massachusetts . ''","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"`` One state .","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"That 's why we have 50 different states .","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"They 're laboratories of democracy , ''","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"Boehner said .","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"Boehner would n't say , however ,","depth":6},{"id":70,"text":"if Romney was facing a credibility problem with voters","depth":7},{"id":71,"text":"who regard his Massachusetts law as the same as Obama 's federal law .","depth":7},{"id":72,"text":"Instead , Boehner reiterated","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"that Romney was just as committed to repealing Obama 's health care law as any Republican .","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"`` Gov . Romney , just like all the rest of us Republicans in Washington , are going to work to repeal Obamacare ,","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"and our resolve is stronger than ever with the passage , or the approval of the Supreme Court . '' -","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"Check out the CNN Electoral Map and Calculator","depth":2},{"id":77,"text":"and game out your own strategy for November .","depth":2}],"relations":[{"parent":155,"left":153,"right":154,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":153,"left":0,"right":152,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"